N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 455.56 - Barber and beauty shop

State Regulations

This functional reporting center must contain all the
expenses associated with providing barber and beautician services to the
patients at the residential health care facility. (a) Standard unit of measure. None. (b) Data source. Not applicable. Notes
